RECOMMENDED IMPLEMENTATION PLAN
================================================================================

PHASE 1: CRITICAL FIXES (2 hours total)
Target: Complete within 1 week

Step 1: Add Stylesheet Links (5 minutes)
- Edit all 6 guide pages
- Add <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../styles.css"> to <head>
- Verify stylesheet path correct (../../ goes to root)

Step 2: Replace Hardcoded Colors (30 minutes)
- Open each file in text editor
- Use Find & Replace for color values
- Perform bulk replacements across all 8 non-compliant files
- Test that colors display correctly

Step 3: Update Font-Family (10 minutes)
- Find: font-family: Georgia, serif;
- Replace: font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;

Step 4: Fix Border-Radius (10 minutes)
- Find: border-radius: 6px;
- Replace: border-radius: var(--radius-md);
- Find: border-radius: 3px;
- Replace: border-radius: var(--radius-sm);

Result after Phase 1: 60% overall compliance


PHASE 2: HIGH PRIORITY FIXES (2 hours total)
Target: Complete within 2 weeks

Step 1: Add Responsive Media Queries (45 minutes)
- Add to each page's <style> block:

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  body { padding: 1rem; font-size: 16px; }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  max-width: 100%;
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  body { padding: 0.5rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  h3 { font-size: 1rem; }
  table { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .guide-item { flex-direction: column; }
}

Step 2: Update Navigation (20 minutes)
- Restructure <nav> to match design system
- Use class names: navbar, nav-container, nav-brand, nav-menu
- Ensure navigation links work with breadcrumb structure

Step 3: Add Transitions (15 minutes)
- Add var(--transition) to interactive elements
- Apply to hover states
- Update link and button hover effects

Result after Phase 2: 85% overall compliance


PHASE 3: MEDIUM PRIORITY (1 hour total)
Target: Complete within 1 month

Step 1: Add Shadows (15 minutes)
- Add var(--shadow) to appropriate cards and sections
- Add var(--shadow-sm) to subtle elevation effects

Step 2: Refine Components (30 minutes)
- Ensure tables use semantic styling
- Update cards to follow design system patterns
- Verify all interactive elements have proper states

Step 3: Final Testing (15 minutes)
- Test all responsive breakpoints
- Verify colors render correctly
- Check transitions work smoothly
- Validate accessibility (contrast, focus states)

Result after Phase 3: 100% overall compliance


